Shell EcoSafe L10 is a fully synthetic, non-aqueous hydraulic fluid that can be used in industrial, marine and mobile equipment, including high-pressure systems, systems with servo valves and all robotics.
Shell EcoSafe L10 is formulated from a high VI, fully synthetic basestock coupled with a non-metallic additive package providing the properties demanded by todayâ€™s high performance hydraulic systems. Shell EcoSafe L10 is readily biodegradable and has excellent low temperature properties, good shear stability, and is resistant to oxidative and thermal degradation.
